title: Carson was Simping, too. Katerino, CallMeCarson, Fitz AND YOU.
description:
It was a fake relationship: Carson didn't "get cheated on" and Katerino didn't cheat on him, because she never was his girlfriend.  Carson was a simp.  All parties need to be cautious as soon as you take that first step into fiction by choosing NOT to reveal that you've already got a boyfriend: most people really can't handle living a lie.
Aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaand we have Discord: https://discord.gg/jfkDWF
